&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conduct employee relations concerns and determine the type of disciplinary actions that will be imposed on certain offenses based on the Company handbook&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible for the overall compliance of the HR solutions and HR Procedures applied at the business assigned.&lt;/p&gt;
